snippet.title: Wedgie Simulator - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
The trailer to our first game, Wedgie Simulator!
The demo is now available on Itch.io and Steam!

Download demo (or pre-order the game) on Itch:
https://underweardemesne.itch.io/wedgie-simulator

Download demo on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1761480/Wedgie_Simulator/
